  "delete_node": "# delete_node\nDelete a node by ID.\nToolset: pages\nWrite: yes (access: edit)\n\nParams:\n  nodeId (string, required) — Node ID to delete",
  "stage_changes": "# stage_changes\nMark nodes as staged (preview). Staged nodes are shown at reduced opacity with an annotation. Use commit_changes to finalize or discard_changes to remove them.\nToolset: staging\nWrite: yes (access: edit)\n\nParams:\n  nodeIds (array, required) — Node IDs to stage",
  "commit_changes": "# commit_changes\nFinalize staged nodes — restores original opacity and removes staging annotations. If no nodeIds provided, commits all currently staged nodes.\nToolset: staging\nWrite: yes (access: edit)\n\nParams:\n  nodeIds (array, optional) — Node IDs to commit (default: all staged)",
  "discard_changes": "# discard_changes\nRemove staged nodes from the canvas entirely. If no nodeIds provided, discards all currently staged nodes.\nToolset: staging\nWrite: yes (access: edit)\n\nParams:\n  nodeIds (array, optional) — Node IDs to discard (default: all staged)",
